OL,5,G0150 Blue Bloods
OL,6,     FWhen Baez discovers a corpse in
OL,7,     Fher front yard, she asks Danny to
OL,8,     Fhelp prove her innocence; Erin
OL,9,     Fstruggles to find a peaceful
OL,10,     Fsolution when she receives harsh
OL,11,     Fcase notes from her boss.
OL,12,G0245 Bull
OL,13,     FBull represents an idealistic,
OL,14,     Fflamboyant judge who is indicted
OL,15,     Ffor Obstruction of Justice after
OL,16,     Fallowing a witness to avoid FBI
OL,17,     Fagents who have arrived to arrest
OL,18,     Fher.
